Introduction

Park Je Up, also known as Jeup and formerly as Seowool, is a South Korean singer under KH Company. He is a member of the boy group IMFACT and the duo D&J.

Jeup made his solo debut on October 3, 2022, with the digital single Daystar. He is also recognized for competing on the reality survival shows The Unit, Sing Again 3, and Build Up: Vocal Boy Group Survivor.
